This patch is to add the missing setting back for asoc encap_port.

Fixes: 8dba29603b5c ("sctp: add SCTP_REMOTE_UDP_ENCAPS_PORT sockopt")
Signed-off-by: Xin Long <lucien.xin@gmail.com>
